  <official_title>A Phase I, Partially Blinded, Randomized, Placebo Controlled, Active Comparator Study to Explore the Safety, Tolerability, Pharmacokinetics and Pharmacodynamics in Post-menopausal Women After Daily Oral Doses of PTH134</official_title>
